overview: What happens when you have to choose between who you are and what you love? Choral singer Ari Agha is faced with this dilemma when they consider testosterone therapy, which could cost them their singing voice. A dire lack of research on the topic makes it an even tougher decision. "Key of T" is the story of their decision, the journey of their voice transition, and what they did with the result.
title: Key of T
